{"tid":695403,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖慎入）喉嚨生瘜肉","createTime":"2018-06-09T07:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T08:22:27.000Z","uid":154221,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7be2e25a1e047a83471d7b0b60aa0a3a978b6783","tid":695403,"uid":154221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"唔煙 唔酒 冇不良嗜好 間中做運動 <br />\n鐘意食熱氣野 常飲咖啡奶茶檸茶 返工輪班返通宵 唔知係咪咁 所以生瘜肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/145907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F145907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8d0b57f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未夠三十歲 我唔知係唔係發炎 瘜肉位置係咽喉定聲帶 唔識分<br />\n訓覺就好似有口水積係咽喉 訓著之前都不斷呑口水 平時日常都成日呑口水 唔痕唔痛 冇痰 口水冇異樣 近啲一年先係咁<br />\n講野講一陣就覺得喉龍有啲累"},{"pid":"1aa59a04aefb364c5e91bba23516185d6f4158b8","tid":695403,"uid":134666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"哇屌你堆白色珍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79bea615e177716267c974379e3ddb68f7b0aa0","tid":695403,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:14:35.000Z","msg":"你個口一定好撚臭 臭撚過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068ece612eaf5741dcd23b724c37d8b206bdc832","tid":695403,"uid":154221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa59a04aefb364c5e91bba23516185d6f4158b8","tid":695403,"uid":134666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"哇屌你堆白色珍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr